Package nl.strohalm.cyclos.services.access.exceptions

Exception Summary
AlreadyConnectedException Indicates that a given user is already connected, while the access settings prevents mutliple connections
BlockedCredentialsException Exception thrown when the given credentials were blocked by tries
CredentialsAlreadyUsedException Exception thrown when an user tries to change his password to some he had already used in past
CredentialsException Base exception for credentials
InactiveMemberException Exception thrown when an inactive member is trying to login
InvalidCardException The given card is invalid
InvalidCredentialsException The given credentials are invalid
InvalidUserForChannelException Exception thrown when an user is trying to access a channel that he/she can't access
LoginException Exception thrown for login exceptions
NotConnectedException Exception thrown when trying to disconnect a member that is no longer logged in
SessionAlreadyInUseException Custom exception thrown when trying to login with a session id already in use
SystemOfflineException Exception thrown when the system is offline and someone without manage online state permission tries to login
SystemOnlineException Exception thrown when the system is online, while it shouldn't be in case of initializing heavy system tasks.
UserNotFoundException
